WEBVTT

00:02:59.846 --> 00:03:03.987
A modern cult, by contrast, separates
its members from others.

00:03:03.987 --> 00:03:07.857
Rather than providing guidelines
for members to live better lives,

00:03:07.857 --> 00:03:10.448
a cult seeks to directly control them,

00:03:10.448 --> 00:03:12.378
from personal and family relationships,

00:03:12.378 --> 00:03:15.777
to financial assets 
and living arrangements.

00:03:15.777 --> 00:03:18.918
Cults also demand obedience 
to human leaders

00:03:18.918 --> 00:03:21.147
who tend to be highly persuasive people

00:03:21.147 --> 00:03:24.178
with authoritarian 
and narcissistic streaks

00:03:24.178 --> 00:03:29.539
motivated by money, sex, power,
or all three.

00:03:29.539 --> 00:03:33.698
